; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">To understand why=
 Ethereum isn&#8217;t going to die, let&#8217;s start with an analogy.&nbsp=
;</p><h3 style=3D"-moz-osx-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-font-smooth=
